   Here's a round-up of coverage in Science News of the American Association for the Advancement of Science annual meeting held February 14-18, 2013 in Boston.

   NEWS STORIES

   Saturday, February 16, 2013

   Bird, human tweets come from similar parts of the brain

   Genetics study finds parallels in birdsong and language.
